import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './Sell.css'; const Sell = () => { const [step, setStep] = useState(1); // Manage which step to show const [userInfo, setUserInfo] = useState({ name: '', surname: '', email: '', password: '', phone: '' }); const [carInfo, setCarInfo] = useState({ make: '', model: '', year: '', price: '', kilometers: '', transmission: '', driveType: '', fuelType: '', exteriorColor: '', interiorColor: '', features: { navigation: false, bluetooth: false, parkingSensors: false, heatedSeats: false }, images: [] }); const handleUserInput = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setUserInfo((prev) => ({ ...prev, [name]: value })); }; const handleCarInput = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setCarInfo((prev) => ({ ...prev, [name]: value })); }; const handleNextStep = () => { setStep((prev) => prev + 1); }; const handlePreviousStep = () => { setStep((prev) => prev - 1); }; return (

); }; export default Sell;
